# Cloudflare Pages redirects (Netlify-compatible syntax).
# Cloudflare reads this file; it ignores netlify.toml.
#
# The promoted build is index.html, which every static host serves at "/"
# automatically — so NO root rewrite is needed (and a root rewrite fought
# Cloudflare's automatic .html clean-URL handling, causing a 308 loop / 522).

# Hide non-promoted builds: old versioned files (/mi-dia-vNN.html) and mockups
# redirect to the homepage. The hyphen means this does NOT match index.html.
# Best-effort on Cloudflare (a splat is a "dynamic" redirect).
/mi-dia-*      /              301
